{
  "stem": "719.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But while we were walking, he said to me, which I'll never forget, he said, you're a brave little girl, aren't you?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We are just here alone, and you trust me, and you go with me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'll never forget those words.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "An 18-year-old-- and he spoke in Polish to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I looked at him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I said, now, what would you do with a piece of nothing?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I said to him that way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he looked at me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I said, look at me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "For 10,000 francs, you can get the nicest, the most beautiful woman in Brussels.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So he clapped me on my shoulder, and said, oh, you're a smart one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I wasn't scared, because I realized if he is a businessman, what would he do?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I mean, 10,000 francs, he could go to any nightclub and enjoy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But when he looked at me, and he talked like that, for a moment, I said, gee, I did have courage, all by myself to come to my aunt's house.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I arrived to my aunt's house, she bought me clothes, and she took me to show me around.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this I must tell you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm almost finished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am impressed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll never forget, as long as my eyes are open, Brussels, Belgium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I hadn't seen real chocolate or oranges or real food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When my uncle took me to a store, and he said to me, you know, that Belgium-- Belgium, in those days, that was about summer of 1946-- said, Belgium was the only country in Europe that didn't suffer as much, maybe because the king was a collaborator.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Later on, they arrested the king of Belgium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His son took the throne.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
